data.description: Welcome to 111 Sunset Ct., Morton, IL! This amazing ranch home features over 2700 finished sqft with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, nestled in a great neighborhood.  The main floor has a large living room, a formal dining with a fireplace, a kitchen with lots of storage, and a laundry room.  The finished basement has a large family room and storage area.  Outside the home features a large homesite with a patio, large driveway leading to a 2 stall attached garage and beautiful landscaping.  The home shows pride of ownership throughout, don't miss out on making yours!
